title: Matthew Bourne's Swan Lake 2012 720p.mkv
description:
Matthew Bourne's contemporary choreography of Tchaikovsky's famous music, first presented to the world in 1995, and it is hence-after a massive hit. This version is taken (ripped) from the Blu-ray disk from the 2012 production.

With:
Richard Winsor (best known from StreetDance 3D)
Dominic North
Nina Goldman
Madelaine Brennan
Steve Kirkham, and
Joseph Vaughan

It is in HD quality (720p) with 5.1 audio.

Enjoy!
